obacco/smoking-and-tobacco-laws-in-australia" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>澳大利亚卫生和老年护理部</em></a>称，“澳大利亚政府对烟草产品征税，通过对烟草产品征收消费税来降低其价格。”</p><p>他们继续说道：“烟草消费税是根据平时平均每周收入（AWOTE）指数化的。这有助于确保烟草产品不会随着时间的推移而变得更加便宜。”</p><p>昆士兰大学公共卫生学院研究主任科拉尔·加特纳（Coral Gartner）教授告诉<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2023/nov/15/tommy-lee-cigarette-prices-australia-motley-crue" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a> ：“澳大利亚在烟草税收水平上符合国际最佳做法，卷烟零售价格的 77% 由税收组成。”</p><p>他继续说：“如果汤米·李访问新西兰，他可能也会惊讶地发现卷烟价格同样高，税收约占零售价的83%。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzsDMJvLHfg/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 5